Title: Last Tango in Halifax-Series 2

reviewText: Wrapping up many of last season's foils, the excellent cast of this British series have picked up where they left off. It's an excellent story about unexpected love and a new definition of what family is.  Esteemed actors Derek Jacobi and Anne Reid  play an elderly widowed couple who find each other again after a missed opportunity as teenagers. They decide to marry quickly, why waste time at their age? The relationship shocks their respective families but both soon come round. This series has a lot of heart and is full of surprises, definitely something for everyone.
Title: Last Tango in Halifax-Series 2

reviewText: Love this drama and the excellent cast of players. The  story line moves at a quick, humorous, and enjoyable pace. The countryside, homes, and car rides provide great backdrops to the characters' conversations. Highly recommend this series. Start Season 1.
